   PLOT (Eng):
   Document name: Doomsday 2012: The End of Days
   There are prophecies and oracles from around the world that all seem to
   point to December 21, 2012 as doomsday. The ancient Mayan Calendar, the
   medieval predictions of Merlin, the Book of Revelation and the Chinese
   oracle of the I Ching all point to this specific date as the end of
   civilization. A new technology called "The Web-Bot Project" makes massive
   scans of the internet as a means of forecasting the future... and has turned
   up the same dreaded date: 2012. Skeptics point to a long history of
   "Failed Doomsdays",but many oracles of doom throughout history have a
   disturbingly accurate track record. As the year 2012 ticks ever closer we'll
   speculate if there are any reasons to believe these doomsayers.
